  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/16/greg-kihn-jeopardy-and-the-breakup-song-singer-dies-at-75.webp" alt="Greg Kihn, 'Jeopardy' and 'The Breakup Song' singer, dies at 75"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Greg Kihn, 'Jeopardy' and 'The Breakup Song' singer, dies at 75</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Greg Kihn, a rock singer who rose to popularity during the 1980s with hits like "The Breakup Song" and "Jeopardy," has died at age 75.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/16/greg-kihn-jeopardy-and-the-breakup-song-singer-dies-at-75/"  >(Jordan Unger, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 21:05:23 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 21:05:23 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Addy Bink, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/19/project-2025-is-anti-american-spokesperson-for-harris-campaign-says.webp" alt="Project 2025 is 'anti-American,' spokesperson for Harris campaign says"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Project 2025 is 'anti-American,' spokesperson for Harris campaign says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Trump has spent months trying to distance himself from Project 2025, but the Harris campaign says the connection is there.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/19/project-2025-is-anti-american-spokesperson-for-harris-campaign-says/"  >(Addy Bink, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:37:37 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:37:37 -0400">
