           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">San Diego's 'strawberry man' gets community support after accident</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Gerardo Rivera, 76, has been selling fruit on the side of the road off Rancho Santa Fe Road for 20 years.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/19/san-diegos-strawberry-man-accident/"  >(Juliette Vara, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 20:37:32 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 20:37:32 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="SUSAN HAIGH and GARY D. ROBERTSON, Associated Press, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/17/hundreds-of-miles-away-hurricane-ernesto-still-affects-us-beaches-with-rip-currents-house-collapse.webp" alt="Hundreds of miles away, Hurricane Ernesto still affects US beaches with rip currents, house collapse"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Hundreds of miles away, Hurricane Ernesto still affects US beaches with rip currents, house collapse</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Even with the storm hundreds of miles offshore, Hurricane Ernesto was still being felt Saturday along much of the U.S. Eastern Seaboard, with dangerous rip currents forcing public beaches to close during one of the final busy weekends of the summer season.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/17/hundreds-of-miles-away-hurricane-ernesto-still-affects-us-beaches-with-rip-currents-house-collapse/"  >(SUSAN HAIGH and GARY D. ROBERTSON, Associated Press, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 19:14:52 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 19:14:52 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Amy Larson, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/16/ufc-star-cain-velasquez-changes-plea-in-vigilante-shooting.webp" alt="UFC&#160;star Cain Velasquez changes plea in 'vigilante' shooting"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">UFC&#160;star Cain Velasquez changes plea in 'vigilante' shooting</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      (KRON) -- Former UFC heavyweight champion Cain Velasquez pleaded no contest to attempted murder on Friday for firing a gun at a man who allegedly molested one of the fighter's young children.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/16/ufc-star-cain-velasquez-changes-plea-in-vigilante-shooting/"  >(Amy Larson, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 19:44:01 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 19:44:01 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Zach Schonfeld, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/17/george-santos-to-plead-guilty-to-multiple-charges-in-fraud-case-monday.webp" alt="George Santos to plead guilty to multiple charges in fraud case Monday"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">George Santos to plead guilty to multiple charges in fraud case Monday</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The plea deal enables Santos to avoid trial next month on 23 criminal charges that could’ve carried significant prison time, if convicted.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/17/george-santos-to-plead-guilty-to-multiple-charges-in-fraud-case-monday/"  >(Zach Schonfeld, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
