        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 21:12:05 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 21:12:05 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/17/turkeys-parliament-descends-chaotic-bloody-brawl-jailed-leader.webp" alt="Turkey&#8217;s parliament descends into chaotic, bloody brawl over jailed opposition leader"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Turkey&#8217;s parliament descends into chaotic, bloody brawl over jailed opposition leader</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Turkey&apos;s parliament broke into a fistfight Friday during a special session about a delegate elected last year after he was jailed for anti-Erdoğan protests.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/17/turkeys-parliament-descends-chaotic-bloody-brawl-jailed-leader/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:17:46 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:17:46 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/19/malawi-receives-an-insurance-payout-of-112-million-for-el-nino-linked-drought-disaster.webp" alt="Malawi receives an insurance payout of $11.2 million for El Nino-linked drought disaster"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Malawi receives an insurance payout of $11.2 million for El Nino-linked drought disaster</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Malawian government has received an insurance payout of $11.2 million for an El Nino-linked drought that led to a disaster declaration in the southern African nation.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/19/malawi-receives-an-insurance-payout-of-112-million-for-el-nino-linked-drought-disaster/"  >(Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 18 Aug 2024 09:12:31 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 18 Aug 2024 09:12:31 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JINTAMAS SAKSORNCHAI, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/18/paetongtarn-shinawatra-becomes-thai-prime-minister-after-royal-signoff.webp" alt="Paetongtarn Shinawatra becomes Thai prime minister after royal signoff"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Paetongtarn Shinawatra becomes Thai prime minister after royal signoff</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BANGKOK (AP) — Paetongtarn Shinawatra, daughter of the divisive former leader Thaksin Shinawatra, became Thailand's prime minister after receiving a royal letter of endorsement Sunday, two days after she was chosen by Parliament following a court order that removed her predecessor.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/18/paetongtarn-shinawatra-becomes-thai-prime-minister-after-royal-signoff/"  >(JINTAMAS SAKSORNCHAI, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:52:53 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:52:53 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/19/israel-accepts-biden-cease-fire-proposal-blinken-calls-hamas-do-same.webp" alt="Blinken says Israel accepts Biden cease-fire proposal, calls on Hamas to do the same"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Blinken says Israel accepts Biden cease-fire proposal, calls on Hamas to do the same</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Secretary of State Blinken says Israel has accepted a cease-fire proposal put forward by the U.S., Egypt and Qatar, though the fighting can only end if Hamas too agrees to the deal.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/19/israel-accepts-biden-cease-fire-proposal-blinken-calls-hamas-do-same/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 18 Aug 2024 12:28:01 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 18 Aug 2024 12:28:01 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Lauren Sforza, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/18/israeli-strikes-kill-19-people-in-gaza-ahead-of-blinken-visit.webp" alt="Israeli strikes kill 19 people in Gaza ahead of Blinken visit"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Israeli strikes kill 19 people in Gaza ahead of Blinken visit</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Israeli strikes killed 19 people in Gaza overnight as Secretary of State Antony Blinken heads to the region to push for a cease-fire and the release of hostages being held by militant group Hamas.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/18/israeli-strikes-kill-19-people-in-gaza-ahead-of-blinken-visit/"  >(Lauren Sforza, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 00:39:37 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 00:39:37 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="RAVI NESSMAN, ZEKE MILLER and AAMER MADHANI, Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/17/diplomacy-intensifies-to-halt-the-israel-hamas-war-and-prevent-wider-regional-conflict.webp" alt="US official says Mideast mediators are preparing for implementation of cease-fire deal in advance"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US official says Mideast mediators are preparing for implementation of cease-fire deal in advance</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      JERUSALEM (AP) — In a sign that mediators believe a Gaza cease-fire deal is imminent, a U.S. official said Friday that Mideast negotiators are working out logistics for the potential release of hostages and distribution of aid as part of any agreement to end the Israel-Hamas war.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/17/diplomacy-intensifies-to-halt-the-israel-hamas-war-and-prevent-wider-regional-conflict/"  >(RAVI NESSMAN, ZEKE MILLER and AAMER MADHANI, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 21:35:21 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 21:35:21 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Patrick Djordjevic, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/16/blinken-israel-ceasefire-talks.webp" alt="Sec. of State Blinken traveling to Israel amid cease-fire talks"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Sec. of State Blinken traveling to Israel amid cease-fire talks</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Blinken intends to reach an accord through the bridging proposal presented today by the U.S., with support from Egypt and Qatar.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/16/blinken-israel-ceasefire-talks/"  >(Patrick Djordjevic, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/tech/">Technology</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 18:04:54 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 18:04:54 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Info World">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/16/string-comparisons-in-java.webp" alt="String comparisons in Java"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">String comparisons in Java</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Java’s String class encapsulates an array of bytes. A byte can be converted to a char, in which case, String becomes an array of characters used to compose words, sentences, or any other data you want.
In this Java challenger, you’ll learn how to compare two Strings for equality.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/16/string-comparisons-in-java/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
