    <h3 itemprop="headline">Write better, faster with these 6 free AI tools</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      If you spend most of your day pecking away at a keyboard, the process of putting together words can become tedious and challenging—even if you’re an otherwise great writer.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/19/best-free-ai-writing-tools/"  >(Doug Aamoth, Fast Company)</a>
