      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/20/joe-bidens-exit-a-civil-rights-hero-and-covid-politics-takeaways-from-day-1-of-the-dnc.webp" alt="Joe Biden's exit, talk of the glass ceiling, a nod to Gaza protesters. Takeaways from DNC's Day 1"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
