    <h3 itemprop="headline">Joe Biden's exit, talk of the glass ceiling, a nod to Gaza protesters. Takeaways from DNC's Day 1</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Democratic National Convention’s first night has showcased speeches from the last Democrat to lose to Donald Trump and the last one to beat him.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/20/joe-bidens-exit-a-civil-rights-hero-and-covid-politics-takeaways-from-day-1-of-the-dnc/"  >(Will Weissert And Nicholas Riccardi, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 16:11:39 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 16:11:39 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/19/harris-campaign-website-still-missing-policy-positions-dnc-kicks-off.webp" alt="Harris campaign website still missing policy positions as DNC kicks off"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris campaign website still missing policy positions as DNC kicks off</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Policy plans or proposals have remained absent from the Harris campaign&apos;s website amid criticism that the Democratic nominee is avoiding the public spotlight.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/19/harris-campaign-website-still-missing-policy-positions-dnc-kicks-off/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
